<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">لِقَوْلِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(الْخَيْلُ مَعْقُودٌ فِي نَوَاصِيهَا الْخَيْرُ إِلَى يَوْمِ الْقِيَامَةِ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>